00:11:37.500 --> 00:11:38.625 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Hadi Robin.

143
00:11:39.208 --> 00:11:40.958 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Batman değil miyim?

144
00:11:44.875 --> 00:11:45.750 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
JUTUL ENDÜSTRİLERİ

145
00:11:45.833 --> 00:11:50.166 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Bu, Jutul Endüstrileri'nin
genel organizasyon şeması.

146
00:11:52.916 --> 00:11:54.875 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
İşlerin %25'i petrolle ilgiliyse

147
00:11:54.958 --> 00:11:58.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
buna deniz sondajı dâhil mi
